tion to the natural landscape beyond. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-white-kitchen-290525-1239-03.jpg 1834w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-white-kitchen-290525-1239-03-940x1312.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-white-kitchen-290525-1239-03-800x1117.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-white-kitchen-290525-1239-03-768x1072.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-white-kitchen-290525-1239-03-1100x1536.jpg 1100w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-white-kitchen-290525-1239-03-1467x2048.jpg 1467w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1834px) 100vw, 1834px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFloating wood stairs by the living room become a sculptural focal point in the home, rising gracefully above a bed of white stones and greenery.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1366\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-stairs-290525-1241-01.jpg\" alt=\"Floating timber stairs by the living room become a sculptural focal point in the home, rising gracefully above a bed of white stones and greenery.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-stairs-290525-1241-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-stairs-290525-1241-01-940x669.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-stairs-290525-1241-01-800x569.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-stairs-290525-1241-01-768x546.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-stairs-290525-1241-01-1536x1093.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-290525-1206-01.jpg\" alt=\"Floating timber stairs by the living room become a sculptural focal point in the home, rising gracefully above a bed of white stones and greenery.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-290525-1206-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-290525-1206-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-290525-1206-01-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-290525-1206-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-290525-1206-01-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eUpstairs, there’s a serene home office designed for focus without rigidity. Natural light bathes the space, highlighting the clean lines of a wood desk setup for two. Woven chairs, a leafy plant, and minimal decor reinforce the balance between functionality and calm.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1516\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-01.jpg\" alt=\"A serene home office designed for focus without rigidity. Natural light bathes the space, highlighting the clean lines of wood desk setup for two. Woven chairs, a leafy plant, and minimal decor reinforce the balance between functionality and calm.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-01-940x742.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-01-800x632.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-01-768x606.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-01-1536x1213.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1837\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02.jpg\" alt=\"A serene home office designed for focus without rigidity. Natural light bathes the space, highlighting the clean lines of wood desk setup for two. Woven chairs, a leafy plant, and minimal decor reinforce the balance between functionality and calm.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02.jpg 1837w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02-940x1310.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02-800x1115.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02-768x1070.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02-1102x1536.jpg 1102w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/minimalist-home-office-290525-1205-02-1470x2048.jpg 1470w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1837px) 100vw, 1837px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn one of the bedrooms, the design of the room is an exercise in restful restraint. Sunlight filters through sliding doors that open onto a balcony surrounded by lush greenery, while soft linen bedding, natural textures, and minimal styling keep the mood grounded. A wood feature wall adds quiet warmth, and sculptural accents, from side tables to abstract art, offer subtle personality within the calm palette. It’s a room designed for retreat, where every element supports peace.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1347\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-01.jpg\" alt=\"The design of this bedroom is an exercise in restful restraint. Sunlight filters through sliding doors that open onto a balcony surrounded by lush greenery, while soft linen bedding, natural textures, and minimal styling keep the mood grounded. A timber feature wall adds quiet warmth, and sculptural accents, from side tables to abstract art, offer subtle personality within the calm palette. It’s a room designed for retreat, where every element supports peace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-01-940x659.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-01-800x561.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-01-768x539.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-01-1536x1078.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1700\" height=\"2091\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02.jpg\" alt=\"The design of this bedroom is an exercise in restful restraint. Sunlight filters through sliding doors that open onto a balcony surrounded by lush greenery, while soft linen bedding, natural textures, and minimal styling keep the mood grounded. A timber feature wall adds quiet warmth, and sculptural accents, from side tables to abstract art, offer subtle personality within the calm palette. It’s a room designed for retreat, where every element supports peace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02.jpg 1700w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02-940x1156.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02-800x984.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02-768x945.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02-1249x1536.jpg 1249w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-02-1665x2048.jpg 1665w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1700px) 100vw, 1700px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1700\" height=\"2185\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03.jpg\" alt=\"The design of this bedroom is an exercise in restful restraint. Sunlight filters through sliding doors that open onto a balcony surrounded by lush greenery, while soft linen bedding, natural textures, and minimal styling keep the mood grounded. A timber feature wall adds quiet warmth, and sculptural accents, from side tables to abstract art, offer subtle personality within the calm palette. It’s a room designed for retreat, where every element supports peace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03.jpg 1700w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03-940x1208.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03-800x1028.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03-768x987.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03-1195x1536.jpg 1195w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bedroom-wood-accent-wall-290525-1203-03-1593x2048.jpg 1593w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1700px) 100vw, 1700px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eClean lines and warm materials define the bathroom’s quiet elegance. A fluted wood vanity adds tactile interest beneath a wide mirror, while stone-look tiles and twin basins enhance the sense of space. Bronze fixtures introduce just a hint of glow, elevating the room without overpowering its simplicity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1528\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-01.jpg\" alt=\"Clean lines and warm materials define the bathroom’s quiet elegance. A fluted timber vanity adds tactile interest beneath a wide mirror, while stone-look tiles and twin basins enhance the sense of space. Bronze fixtures introduce just a hint of glow, elevating the room without overpowering its simplicity.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-01-940x748.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-01-800x637.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-01-768x611.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-01-1536x1222.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1851\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02.jpg\" alt=\"Clean lines and warm materials define the bathroom’s quiet elegance. A fluted timber vanity adds tactile interest beneath a wide mirror, while stone-look tiles and twin basins enhance the sense of space. Bronze fixtures introduce just a hint of glow, elevating the room without overpowering its simplicity.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02.jpg 1851w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02-940x1300.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02-800x1106.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02-768x1062.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02-1111x1536.jpg 1111w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-bathroom-floating-wood-vanity-280525-1159-02-1481x2048.jpg 1481w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1851px) 100vw, 1851px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis home in Calpe shows how thoughtful design can feel both modern and deeply human. With natural materials, soft light, and clean lines, every space invites calm and connection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://eugenipons.com/\"\u003eEugeni Pons\u003c/a\u003e | Architecture: \u003ca href=\"https://pascualginer.com/web/\"\u003ePasqual Giner Arquitectura\u003c/a\u003e | Interior Design: \u003ca href=\"https://aunoncabrerainteriorismo.com/\"\u003eAunon Cabrera\u003c/a\u003e | Builder: Coinver. Promociones y Construcciones\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
